## Overview

SkillSnap AI uses a multi-layered scoring system to evaluate candidates. Each score component is calculated independently and then combined into a final fit score using dynamic weights based on job category.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    FINAL FIT SCORE (0-100)                     │
│                                                                 │
│   = (ATS × w1) + (GitHub × w2) + (Proof × w3) + (Quality × w4) │
│     + (Experience × w5) + (Link × w6)                          │
│                                                                 │
│   where weights depend on job category                         │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

