## 1. ATS Score Calculation

**File:** `src/lib/scoring.ts`, `src/lib/batch-processor.ts`

### Formula

```
ATS Score = (Skill Match × 0.35) + (Tool Match × 0.25) + (Soft Match × 0.10) 
          + (Experience Match × 0.15) + (Keyword Density × 0.15)
```

### Component Breakdown

| Component | Weight | Description |
|-----------|--------|-------------|
| Skill Match | 35% | Technical skills match percentage |
| Tool Match | 25% | Tools/technologies match percentage |
| Soft Match | 10% | Soft skills match percentage |
| Experience Match | 15% | Experience years vs requirement |
| Keyword Density | 15% | Overall keyword match rate |

### Priority-Weighted Matching

Skills are weighted by priority level:

| Priority | Weight Multiplier |
|----------|-------------------|
| Critical | 2.0x |
| Preferred | 1.0x |
| Bonus | 0.5x |

**Partial matches receive 50% credit.**

### Experience Match Calculation

```javascript
if (experienceYears >= requiredExperience) {
    experienceMatch = 100
} else if (experienceYears >= requiredExperience * 0.7) {
    experienceMatch = 70
} else if (experienceYears >= requiredExperience * 0.5) {
    experienceMatch = 50
} else {
    experienceMatch = 30
}
```

### Weighted Match Percentage Formula

```javascript
weightedPercent = (Σ matchedWeight + Σ partialWeight × 0.5) / Σ totalWeight × 100
```

