## 5. Project Depth Score

**File:** `src/lib/analysis.ts`

### Formula

```javascript
complexity = starScore + languageScore + activityScore + sizeScore + docScore
```

### Component Breakdown

| Component | Formula | Max Points |
|-----------|---------|------------|
| Stars | `min(totalStars × 3, 25)` | 25 |
| Languages | `min(languages.length × 5, 25)` | 25 |
| Active Repos | `min(activeRepos × 5, 25)` | 25 |
| Repo Size | Tiered (see below) | 25 |
| Documentation | Tiered (see below) | 10 |

**Maximum: 110 → capped at 100**

### Repo Size Scoring

```javascript
if (totalRepoSize > 5000 KB) sizeScore = 25
else if (totalRepoSize > 1000 KB) sizeScore = 15
else if (totalRepoSize > 500 KB) sizeScore = 10
else sizeScore = 5
```

### Documentation Scoring

```javascript
if (reposWithDescription > 5) docScore = 10
else if (reposWithDescription > 2) docScore = 5
else docScore = 0
```

### Deep vs Surface Projects

```javascript
deepProjects = min(
    (originalRepos × 0.3) + (totalStars / 10) + (reposWithDescription × 0.2),
    originalRepos
)
surfaceProjects = max(0, originalRepos - deepProjects)
```

### Recommendation Logic

| Complexity | Recommendation |
|------------|----------------|
| ≥ 70 | "Strong technical depth. Ready for complex projects." |
| ≥ 40 | "Moderate depth. May need mentoring on complex architecture." |
| < 40 | "Limited project complexity. Consider technical assessment." |

