## 6. Final Fit Score

**File:** `src/lib/analysis.ts`

### Dynamic Weights by Job Category

| Component | Technical | Creative | General |
|-----------|-----------|----------|---------|
| ATS Score | 30% | 20% | 40% |
| GitHub Score | 25% | 0% | 0% |
| Proof Score | 20% | 0% | 0% |
| Quality Score | 15% | 30% | 10% |
| Experience | 10% | 10% | 20% |
| Link Score | 0%* | 40% | 30% |

*Technical roles get a 5% **bonus** for valid links (not weighted)

### Formula

```javascript
finalScore = (atsScore × weights.ats) +
             (githubScore × weights.github) +
             (proofScore × weights.proof) +
             (qualityScore × weights.quality) +
             (experienceBonus × weights.experience) +
             (linkScore × weights.link)

// Technical roles: Add link bonus
if (jobCategory === "technical" && linkScore > 0) {
    finalScore += (linkScore × 0.05)
}

// Experience bonus
experienceBonus = experienceMatch ? 100 : 50
```

