## 7. ML Predictions

**File:** `src/lib/ml/predictions.ts`

### 7.1 Success Prediction

```javascript
successProbability = (
    (atsScore × 0.20) +
    (githubScore × 0.20) +
    (proofScore × 0.15) +
    (qualityScore × 0.10) +
    (min(experienceYears × 10, 100) × 0.15) +
    (skillMatchPercentage × 0.15) +
    (velocityScore × 0.05)
) / 100
```

### 7.2 Retention Prediction

Base probability: **70%**

| Factor | Adjustment |
|--------|------------|
| Experience ≥ 5 years | +10% |
| Career Switcher | -10% |
| Velocity ≥ 60 | +5% |
| Skill Match < 50% | -15% |

**Range: 30% - 95%**

### 7.3 Growth Potential

Base score: **50**

| Indicator | Adjustment |
|-----------|------------|
| Velocity ≥ 70 | +20 |
| Velocity ≥ 40 | +10 |
| Early Career | +15 |
| GitHub ≥ 60 | +10 |
| Quality ≥ 70 | +5 |

**Trajectory:**
- High: Score ≥ 70
- Moderate: Score ≥ 45
- Low: Score < 45

### 7.4 Ramp-Up Estimate

Base: **6 weeks**

| Factor | Adjustment |
|--------|------------|
| Skill Match ≥ 80% | -2 weeks |
| Skill Match < 50% | +2 weeks |
| Experience ≥ 5 years | -1 week |
| Experience < 2 years | +2 weeks |
| Velocity ≥ 60 | -1 week |

**Range: 2 - 12 weeks**

